PM Agent writes daily assignment drafts here at 02:00. The 09:00 emailer
reads them and sends via Resend.

Layout:
  assignments/
    _TEMPLATE.md                              # email template (mustache placeholders)
    <YYYY-MM-DD>/
      urvi.md                                 # drafted by PM at 02:00
      yasha.md                                # drafted by PM at 02:00
    .email-log-<YYYY-MM-DD>.txt               # one line per send (audit + cap)

Body files use RFC822-style headers — see scripts/send_email.sh.
